		{
			dependencies: ["08BE7B461CC437CA"]
			description: [
				"Once you make a tool, it's parts can be replaced and swapped out. You made a flint pick earlier, try adding the new iron head to it now."
				""
				""
				"Sand Casts are the cheapest way to make casts, place the cast into the Casting Table, and then a stone or wooden part onto the sand cast, then remove the part, this makes a cast of whatever part you used. Permanent Casts can be made by pouring liquid gold onto a part (Hint: Try an Ingot!)"
			]
