		{
			dependencies: ["1BA8589B69D3D94E"]
			description: [
				"Your handmade tools do not shatter in your hands when they break like normal tools, They simply become worn down and unusable. But! They can be repaired!"
				""
				""
				"In a Tinker's Station, combining the tool with the correct repair material (Whatever the head is made from) will repair it. You can also repair an item on the go with a repair kit."
