			description: [
				"It's time to make the Smeltery!"
				""
				"You will need quite a bit of Grout to make a forge large enough to be of use. The Multiblock is created by building a 3x3 base, and building up the walls around it, you do not need corners. You can place the Controller and the Fuel Tank wherever you please within the walls. But I recommend they're easily accssesable. "
				""
				""
				"(Tip: You're going to need Lava to Fuel the Smeltery, It's a good idea to have some sort of generator to keep it running!)"
